### Lab Metadata Endpoint
### Returns lab metadata information based on lab number query parameter
### Route: GET /api/metadata?labNumber={labNumber}

# Environment Variables
# Local development (Azure Functions default)
@baseUrl = http://localhost:7176

# Aspire Service Discovery URI (for service-to-service calls)
# @baseUrl = https+http://_http.api

# Azure Container Apps deployment
# @baseUrl = https://api.thankfulgrass-04b7ad9d.uksouth.azurecontainerapps.io

### GET Lab Metadata - Valid Lab Number
### Expected: 200 OK with LabMetadataDto JSON
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metadata?labNumber=LAB001
Accept: application/json

###

### GET Lab Metadata - Another Valid Lab Number
### Expected: 200 OK with different generated metadata
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metadata?labNumber=LAB002
Accept: application/json

###

### GET Lab Metadata - Not Found Case
### Expected: 404 Not Found (LAB999 is hardcoded to return NotFound)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metadata?labNumber=LAB999
Accept: application/json

###

### GET Lab Metadata - Missing Lab Number (Bad Request)
### Expected: 400 Bad Request with error message
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/metadata
Accept: application/json

###
